title: Reed Hansen's Battle Falls | The Whole Story Wakeskate
description:
Reed Hansen's wakeskate visions come true, in this epic story of the trials and tribulations of Battle Falls build, the event, and many awesome sessions that build within this piece.

Reed joined forces with master cinematographers Sean Kilgus of BFY productions, creator of http://defythemovie.com/, and Fox team wakeskate athlete and Dieter Humpsch, Creator of http://noisiavision.tv/ to bring you the whole story of Reed's epic vision using the unbelievable RED cameras.
